Privacy Policy

Introduction

Welcome to Strength Gadget! We value the trust ye place in us when ye provide us with yer personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect yer information. Our goal is to provide ye a robust service while respecting yer privacy and upholding the highest standards of data protection.

Information Collection

When ye use Strength Gadget, we may collect the following types of information:

Personal Information: This includes yer email address and any other information ye choose to provide when setting up yer account. We use this information to manage yer account and communicate with ye.
Telemetry Data: To improve yer experience and the overall quality of our app, we collect telemetry data related to how ye use our app, such as usage frequency and feature preferences. Collecting this data helps us to better understand yer needs and to optimize our service.
Device Information: We may collect information about the devices ye use to access our app, including hardware models, operating system versions, unique device identifiers, and mobile network information.
Use of Information

The information we collect helps us to provide, maintain, and improve our services. Specifically, we use yer information to:

Operate and improve the app's functionalities;
Understand and analyze how ye use our app to ensure technical functionality, develop new products, and improve your overall user experience;
Communicate with ye about new features, updates, or promotional offers that may be of interest to ye;
Detect and address technical issues and prevent fraud or abuse of our services.
Sharing of Information

We may share yer information with third parties in the following ways:

With service providers who perform services on our behalf, such as hosting, data analysis, information technology, customer service, email delivery, and auditing services.
As necessary, if we believe that there has been a violation of our Terms of Service or to protect the property, rights, and safety of Strength Gadget, its users, or the public.
We may also share aggregated or de-identified information which cannot reasonably be used to identify you.
Security of Information

We be committed to protectin' the security of yer personal information. We implement industry-standard security measures designed to protect yer data from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no security system be infallible, and we cannot guarantee the absolute security of yer information.

Your Rights

Ye have the right to access, update, or delete yer personal information at any time. If ye wish to exercise these rights, please contact us directly through the app or via the contact information below.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time in response to changing legal, technical, or business developments. When we update our Privacy Policy, we will take appropriate measures to inform ye, consistent with the significance of the changes we make.
